            <p><b>2. Aftermarket Sale Fees:</b> A 3% fee is applied to all aftermarket sales of Trraform assets, such as Plots and Subplots, conducted through secondary marketplaces or similar services. This fee is used to support the ongoing development and operation of the Trraform platform. This fee is enforced through the ERC-721C token standard.</p>
